Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:08.23,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(590,200)\fad(800,800)}干\N劲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是各种没干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是高中生哦  而且还是新学期哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干劲什么的只要去做就自然会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是连「去做」的干劲都拿不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样才能拿出「去做」这样的干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「去做」的干劲吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  总之就得去干！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想做一个单纯的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  差不多该起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:54.16,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的早饭是烤鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我要吃蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是吃过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼里面可是有大量营养的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑食的话可是长不大…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那可是我们重要的早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不…不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可绝对不是机器人般的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定那只猫也有着自己的难处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撞上了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H0F0F0F&\bord0\fs35}小芥子人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小芥子人偶（こけし）江户时代末期开始出现的日本东北地区的温泉特产及乡土玩具\N一般形态为球形头部和圆柱形身子，没有四肢。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H0F0F0F&\bord0\fs35}红牛玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}红牛玩偶（赤べこ）福岛县会津地区的乡土玩具，「べこ」是东北方言「牛」的意思\N整体涂红，头部会摆动，是祝愿小孩子茁壮成长的吉祥物。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H0F0F0F&\bord0\fs35}鲑鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Selamat pagi:印尼语早上好的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  祐子  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  我忘记带学生证了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  Selamat pagi被无视了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不想被高年级学生叫出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种时候  只要说「我是三年级学生」不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可解决不了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  打雷？  明明是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会突然掉下什么东西来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是雷阵雨  冰雹之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芥子人偶…从天而降了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会是小芥子人偶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳  这是从哪儿掉下来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啦  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在人生中被小芥子人偶砸到的几率很小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎没有不是吗  那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近于零了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来说  也许会走运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走运个头啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会是红牛玩偶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红牛玩偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  并不是没有走运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样想就行了  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有被生鲜的东西砸到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想来  那可真是不幸中的万幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鲑鱼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你在看什么书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房地产的情报杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  麻衣要搬家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  Selamat pagi又被无视了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 今天要在之后唱摇篮曲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Selamat malam:印尼语晚上好的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat malam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你应该说Selamat pagi才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  什么语言？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班…班会要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  今早来学校的时候  发现这个在鞋箱里面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁知道是谁放进去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  要是有谁知道的话  请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  会是谁呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那种事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是恶作剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是喜欢老师的学生之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不会放弥勒菩萨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  我也不是无法了解那种暗恋的仰慕之情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像美绪对笹原学长的思念一样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士一定在担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小炭炉点着火放在那里也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  下不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  筷子不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木屐也不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  连手也没了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我会被别人发现是机器人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:31.59,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,300)\fad(800,0)\fs25}W\No\Nn\Nd\Ne\Nr\Nf\Nu\Nl
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  再不快点吃的话就要打午休铃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你不喜欢吃小香肠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃便当的时候把最美味的留在最后这是基本常识哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是用「美味」作结束语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来  我要开动啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.33,title-W,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,290)\fad(800,800)}日\N常\N之\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早得很呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…出局了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  美绪  三秒规则哦  三秒规则
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你那是彻彻底底出局了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子是笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出你满满的能量哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:21.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}甩绳者头戴的是中之条家的大福头套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入春季  新的一年就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气候还在持续寒冷中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是比同学们要冷得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:41.65,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(490,160)\fad(600,0)}日常之3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之希望大家不要感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  这是大家与校长我的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家不听我的话  校长我就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去别的学校当别人的校长了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  交头接耳会被批评的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么  校长没有意识到自己的冷笑话太老土了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都没有人笑  他自己应该是最清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  难讲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是想把  明知道大家没有笑还在不断努力的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现给现在的年轻人们看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那样  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位校长…就太厉害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是对那种老头儿冷笑话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我是第一次看到麻衣笑得这么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  这里让我来吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有种一开口就会失去一切的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在她发现之前…还是不要拿下来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}触手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来有请樱井老师为大家进行辅导
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井老师  交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  樱井老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我是学生辅导员樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这么多人面前会紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多久都无法接近我成为理想中的教师的目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说的时候  就要一股脑儿说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在学校经常看到山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家不要把山羊带到学校来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山羊  山羊有什么错！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑山羊来上学并没有违反校规不是吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  啊  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪  那不是笹原学长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜  那就…那就允许骑山羊来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驳回啦  驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部驳回！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能够带山羊来上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那样说  立花美里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我要用我尊贵的双足走着上学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  笹原家的长男可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原家的长男算什么玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们家不过是普通农家罢了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样  长男说自己是长男有什么不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  笹原家里原来是农家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有种被骗了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只停在自行车场的山羊  原来是笹原学长带来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑着白色山羊的笹原学长…来迎接我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  new  year
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me  Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  边骑自行车边打手机是非常危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…最后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上我在自己的鞋箱里发现了弥勒菩萨像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这种恶作剧是不可取的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒菩萨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  请不要突然停下来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这处  说不定就是所谓的既视感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会生气的  请举起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有人承认的话  今天的早会就一直开下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  因为我听说今天是樱井老师的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒菩萨像是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:08.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}5-7-5的俳句格式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为会很适合  而送出礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果弥勒菩萨像  被完全抛弃  by校长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么早会到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢我们校长至今为止的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教导主任！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:29.25,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,250)\fad(600,800)}按\N钮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个消防栓的按钮看上去很有想去按的魔力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  噗噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你试着按一下吧  之前按的时候没有发出声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  要逃出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  总之先到学校空地上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙推什么推啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在推我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前早就看你这家伙不顺眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵了  也许会有人死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:17:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逃了再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吵等下再吵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:09.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}Helvetica Standard：日常原作者あらゐけいいち以自己的同人社团「ヒマラヤイルカ」的\N名义创作的同人志2009年8月23日发行，内容为WEB日记漫画「Helvetica Standard」的总集篇。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  请问KY是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  KY到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  请告诉我KY方面的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  队长  KY是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}KY为空気が読めない的略写，即不解风情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:43.66,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,340)\fad(300,0)\fs30}重\N要\N的\N事\N与\N该\N做\N的\N事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年B班笹原幸治郎同学  请火速到办公室富冈老师处来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说确实是没有违反校规
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是山羊也太那啥了吧  山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有别的办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意徒步的话  骑自行车也是可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不是山羊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫富冈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富冈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加上老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  你就不能不叫它山羊  叫它笹原小次郎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在它还是羊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:22.94,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,290)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N4
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫做东云名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和我一起生活的博士制造出的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士好像在进行着某种研究  整天都待在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我照顾着博士  度过着每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  牛奶冲好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么出众的功能却有痛觉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博…博士  碰到小趾了  碰到小趾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小趾…趾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这样就应该没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有出众的功能小趾却能摘下来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  这个发条是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  还没有转过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时会转转看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样转的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  看来我有很多出众的功能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  很有趣对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非就只是为了这个而装了发条…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非就只是为了这个而装了发条？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把发条取下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为装了发条很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的  请马上摘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…明明很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能变得更加普通就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像普通人一样坐在椅子上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉的时候可以随意翻身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  连学校都没法去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不做成人形机器人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的  我是骗你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也就是芥川龙之介赏，是为了纪念日本文豪芥川龙之介而设立的文学奖项
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去给我拿个芥川奖来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要芥川奖  我要芥川奖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}就是这样的日常风景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是名乃的大拇趾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容量为1GB
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好的容量大小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请期待下回的日常第二话
