Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:42.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闪闪发光  I DO fall in love！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好像能在天空飞翔般
